<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4454397>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–9. Thaioasca contaminata Wang, Xu & Qin sp. nov. 1. male adult (abdomen removed), dorsal view; 2. male adult (abdomen removed), left lateral view; 3. head and thorax, dorsal view; 4. face; 5. forewing; 6. hind wing; 7. abdominal apodeme; 8. male genitalia, left lateral view; 9. male genitalia, dorsal view. Scale bars= 0.5 mm (Figs 1–9)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4454397/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4454399>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10–17. Thaioasca contaminata Wang, Xu & Qin sp. nov. 10. male genitalia, left lateral view; 11. pygofer lobe with ventral appendage, left lateral view; 12. pygofer, dorsal view; 13. subgenital plates; 14. style; 15. aedeagus, left lateral view; 16. aedeagus, dorsal view; 17. anal tube, left lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4454399/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

